section.div: A PyTorch Implementation of RL-DiVTS from "Selecting a Diverse Set of Aesthetically-Pleasing and Representative Video Thumbnails Using Reinforcement Learning" (accepted for publication in the 2023 Int. Conf. on Image Processing)
A python pandas wrapper for the Ergast F1 API
A PyTorch implementation of our attention-based method for explainable video summarization, presented in "Explaining video summarization based on the focus of attention" (IEEE ISM 2022)
This repository contains the source code for my MSc thesis named: Video summarization leveraging Contrastive Learning
